# 💪 AI Physique Analyzer

An AI-powered web application that analyzes body physique from an image and provides personalized workout recommendations using deep learning and similarity search.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧠 Body Type Classification (Ectomorph, Mesomorph, Endomorph)
- 🖼 Image-based analysis using CNN (ResNet)
- 🔍 Similar Physique Search using Embeddings
- 🏋️ Personalized Workout Recommendations
- ⚡ FastAPI Backend
- 🎯 Streamlit Frontend
- 🔗 End-to-End ML Pipeline

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** FastAPI
- **Frontend:** Streamlit
- **ML/DL:** PyTorch, Torchvision
- **Similarity Search:** FAISS
- **Image Processing:** Pillow
- **API Communication:** Requests

---

