## ⚙️ Installation

1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-physique-pro.git
cd ai-physique-pro

2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows

3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
🧠 Train Model
python backend/train.py
🔍 Generate Embeddings
python backend/generate_embeddings.py
🚀 Run Backend
uvicorn backend.main:app --reload

API Docs:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

🎯 Run Frontend
streamlit run frontend/app.py

App URL:
http://localhost:8501

📸 Usage
Upload a body image
Click Analyze

Get:
Body Type
Workout Plan
Similar Physiques

⚠️ Notes
If model is not trained, system will use random predictions
Ensure model.pth and embeddings.npy exist for full functionality

🌟 Future Improvements
